race.description: Book Your Xmas Party Trackside 21/12 Handicap
race.comment: Open race to close out the card. YEAH COPY (3) has placed five from seven over this track and trip and will be rock-hard fit for this contest. Drawn to get a gun run in transit from the inside alley and looks very hard to toss in this line-up. RESOLUTE LADY (7) is a bit hit or miss but saves her best form for this circuit and rates a genuine top-three prospect on the back of her most recent performance. Former NSW galloper SWEETPEA MOOCHI (2) may have suffered from the dreaded second-up syndrome last time out but will find this easier than what he faced down south. Top-three commodity. PRETTY LITTLE LASS (8) will be at peak fitness now and can improve sharply on recent efforts. MILAGRO (11) strips fitter second-up from the spell and may trouble the judge with any luck in running.
